cu.explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP address to an unreachable IP will cause routing failures and prevent CU-AMF communication.

du.explanation_en: Setting T1a_cp_dl to [0, 0] causes timing misalignment in downlink compression, leading to synchronization failures and data transmission errors.
du.explanation_zh: 將 T1a_cp_dl 設定為 [0, 0] 會導致下行壓縮中的時序錯位，造成同步失敗和數據傳輸錯誤。
